user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: Had a wonderful and refreshing meeting with Dhanush. He has unleashed the power of communicating unconventionally with the masses.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: The swift and firm action of the Chief Minister is commendable. The heroic actions by the 3 deceased staff members also needs recognition.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: My sympathies go out to the families of patients and the three staff members that have lost their lives in an attempt to rescuing patients.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: Doctors and attendants allegedly leaving patients to die unattended in these circumstances is unbelievable and deserves condemnation.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: Every doctor and staff member should be primarily concerned with the well being of patients with a responsibility for caring treatment.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: All hospitals' primary mandate should be to save the lives of patients, and should not be driven by making extraordinary profits.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: The recent events in the hospital in Kolkata, resulting in the deaths of several patients is deplorable and inexcusable.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: We should provide the motivation and the opportunity for these successful people to make their rightful contribution with due recognition.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: Many of them want to give back to India their expertise and knowledge. Doctors, scientists and technologists are our greatest ambassadors.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: I visited the new hospital at UCLA and feel proud to see many young Indian doctors in significant positions.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: Political differences and vested interests should never be allowed to stand in the way of India's economic progress.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: It would be a question of national pride for every Indian to rebuild the past glory and reestablish the country's economic leadership.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: We should never let the extraordinary momentum achieved or the global visibility we had diminish.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: India's growth rate has dropped to 6.9%. The manufacturing growth dropped to 2.7% -  a two year low!
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: Forces thought they would knock us down but instead they created a city of heroes.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: We should all find our private space to recall the events of 26/11/2008.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: As I go home at the end of this momentous week, I will fondly remember all the good wishes and kind sentiments expressed by so many.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: I look forward to my retirement while I am still active and pursue many interests that I enjoy but have not had time to undertake.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: I am very pleased and committed to achieve a smooth and seamless transition to my successor. Cyrus is a very good choice for the job.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: Finding a worthwhile successor has been an important milestone and this milestone was achieved yesterday.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: I have been with the Tata Group since 1962. The years have been exciting and interesting.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: Enjoyed meeting the students of UH hotel school. Impressed by their intelligence and great spirit. I wish all of them all the very best.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: Privileged to meet the vibrant Indian community in Houston. Great entrepreneurs who have made their mark on Houston.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: Most impressed by Renu Khator, President of University of Houston. Makes all Indians proud.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: His creativity and innovation has changed the way we live. He will be deeply mourned and greatly missed.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata

text: Steve Jobs has been one of the greatest icons of the Modern Age. His untimely death is a huge loss to us all.
user.description: Chairman Emeritus, Tata Sons. Chairman, Tata Trusts
user.name: Ratan N. Tata
